			<description><![CDATA[<p>
The1stMovement (T1M) is looking for Experienced Freelance Interactive Producers to work with our Production Team. The Production team is responsible for the day to day workings of all projects undertaken by The1stMovement.&nbsp;</p>
<p>
<strong>Production Team Responsibilities</strong></p>
<p>
Planning:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Plan and prioritize to ensure project delivery and Account Management support</li>
<li>
Client-facing&nbsp;communication necessary to coordinate day-to-day logistics may be required</li>
<li>
Develop and update deliverables related to project management including timelines, budgets and workflow process</li>
<li>
Provide ongoing reporting to client/Account Management in the form of status reports, budget reports, traffic/performance reports, etc.</li>
<li>
Be able to identify and resolve risks that impact project completion, initiate action to identify and resolve problems, and ensure goals are met</li>
<li>
Work with department heads to adjust resources as necessary, provide work direction and feedback to all team members and assist in issue resolution</li>
</ul>
<p>
<span style="font-size: 12px;">Management:</span></p>
<ul>
<li>
Asset management, proofreading and project management tools management</li>
<li>
Monitor internal project progress, deliverables and quality assurance.&nbsp; Report status to Director of Account Services and/or associated Account Directors</li>
<li>
Ensure all internal team members are tracking and logging hours on a weekly basis</li>
<li>
Manage all project&nbsp;deliverables</li>
<li>
Provide guidance to team members on communication and technical problems</li>
</ul>
<p>
Financial:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Ensure all projects are delivered according to scope, budget and timeline requirements</li>
<li>
<span style="font-size: 12px;">Manage the project budget and schedule</span></li>
</ul>
<p>
<span style="font-size: 12px;">Quality Control:</span></p>
<ul>
<li>
Adhere to The1stMovement&rsquo;s strict quality control standards</li>
<li>
Ensures all team members are meeting and exceeding development objectives and timelines</li>
</ul>
<p>
Other Skill Requirements:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Must be able to &quot;multitask&quot; and meet short deadlines in a fast-paced environment</li>
<li>
Strong communication skills</li>
<li>
Strong attention to detail, organization and time management</li>
<li>
<span style="font-size: 12px;">Participate in project postmortem sessions</span></li>
<li>
Performs other related duties as indicated in contract</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong style="font-size: 12px;">Requirements</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Previous experience as a<span style="font-size: 12px;">&nbsp;contract/freelance Project Manager/Producer in an Agency or Non-agency environment is required</span></li>
<li>
<span style="font-size: 12px;">A comprehensive technical understanding of interactive process, budgeting, scheduling and managem</span></li>
</ul>
<p>
<span style="font-size: 12px;">​</span><span style="font-size: 12px;">This is a freelance/contract position. &nbsp;Qualified and experienced applicants only. &nbsp;No phone calls.</span></p>
<ul>
</ul>
]]></description>
